Thumper Fathom training digest

Thumper synced Fathom meeting recorder content for <%= @date.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %>.
The calls are stored in WIZWIKI and queued for Qwen embeddings so /ask can retrieve today's conversations.

Training stats
--------------
Calls scanned: <%= @result["call_count"].to_i %>
Created: <%= @result["created"].to_i %>
Updated: <%= @result["updated"].to_i %>
Unchanged: <%= @result["unchanged"].to_i %>
Errors: <%= @result["errors"].to_i %>
Training time: <%= @duration_label %>

Status: <%= @result["errors"].to_i.zero? ? "clean sync with no Fathom errors" : "#{@result["errors"].to_i} sync error(s) need review" %>.

